{
  "texts": [
    "Data retention is limited to the period necessary for the research, after which it is securely destroyed.",
    "The research maintains a principle of transparency and honesty throughout.",
    "The findings are reported with integrity, acknowledging limitations, and presenting data accurately without manipulation or misrepresentation.",
    "The research process, findings, and interpretations are documented meticulously, ensuring that they are verifiable and replicable.",
    "Ensuring that participants are not subjected to harm, whether physical, psychological, or professional, is paramount."
  ]
}